<?xml version="1.1" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<slideshow>
	<documentinfo>
		<author>Jim Dee</author>
		<version>1.1</version>
    	<title>Butternut Squash Soup</title>
		<comment>The reader should remember that seasonal produce will make the best soups. More often than not, local produce is better than foreign alternatives, particularly with short season vegetables. I had the misfortune to try Peruvian asparagus in the middle of September last year, and it is not a product I will endorse here. Nearly every recipe here will require vegetable oil, salt and pepper, so they are omitted from the ingredients list. I recommend Maldon salt, which is widely available, and to my mind is one of the best salts in the world.
		 	</comment>
		<cook>20 min</cook>
		<prep>5 min</prep>
		<price>£3</price>
		<veg>Yes</veg>
		<width>1440</width>
		<height>900</height>
	</documentinfo>
	<defaults>
		<backgroundcolor>#FFFFFF</backgroundcolor>
		<font>Helvetica Neue Thin</font>
		<fontsize>24</fontsize>
		<linecolor>#000000</linecolor>
		<fontcolor>#000000</fontcolor>
		<fillcolor>#CCCCCC</fillcolor>
	</defaults>
	<ingredients>
		<ingredient name="butternut squash" amount="1" units="whole" />
		<ingredient name="butter" amount="25" units="grams" />
	</ingredients>

	<slide id="0" duration="20" lastSlide="false">
		<text xstart="10" ystart="10" xend="1100" yend="300" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="40" fontcolor="#000000" orientation="0"> 
			<textbody underlined="false" bold="true" italic="false">
        		<textstring>Butternut Squash Soup</textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>
		<text xstart="15" ystart="70" xend="1425" yend="300" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="30" fontcolor="#000000" orientation="0"> 
			<textbody underlined="false" bold="false" italic="false">
        		<textstring>This is a soup which simply celebrates the squash, so it important to buy a good quality one. If you are partial to garlic or any particular herb, you can add it at the roasting stage. 

Please click 'Next' or press the right arrow key to begin.</textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>
		
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/IMG_butnut_0.png" xstart="250" ystart="260" width="900" height="600" layer="1" />	
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/slideBackground.png" xstart="0" ystart="0" width="1440" height="900" layer="0" />	
		
	</slide>

	<slide id="1" duration="30" lastSlide="false">
		<text xstart="10" ystart="10" xend="1000" yend="300" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="40" fontcolor="#000000" orientation="0"> 
			<textbody underlined="false" bold="true" italic="false">
        		<textstring>Step One</textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>
		<text xstart="15" ystart="70" xend="1300" yend="200" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="30" fontcolor="#000000" orientation="0"> 
			<textbody underlined="false" bold="false" italic="false">
        		<textstring>Begin by peeling the squash with a sharp knife, reserving the trimmings in a pan. </textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>  
		<text xstart="150" ystart="550" xend="1000" yend="475" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="30" fontcolor="#000000" orientation="0"> 
			<textbody underlined="false" bold="false" italic="false">
        		<textstring>Set the seeds aside as well.</textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>     		
        		
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/IMG_butnut_1.png" xstart="100" ystart="120" width="550" height="366" layer="2" />	
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/IMG_butnut_2.png" xstart="750" ystart="120" width="550" height="366" layer="2" />		
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/IMG_butnut_3.png" xstart="550" ystart="525" width="550" height="366" layer="2" />		
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/slideBackground.png" xstart="0" ystart="0" width="1440" height="900" layer="0" />
		<audio urlname="http://ystv.co.uk/~john.caine/swengrepo/sample2.mp3" starttime="5" loop="false" />		
	</slide>

	<slide id="2" duration="30" lastSlide="false">
		<text xstart="10" ystart="10" xend="1000" yend="300" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="40" fontcolor="#000000" > 
			<textbody underlined="false" bold="true" italic="false">
        		<textstring>Step Two</textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>
		<text xstart="15" ystart="70" xend="1400" yend="600" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="30" fontcolor="#000000" > 
			<textbody underlined="false" bold="false" italic="false">
        		<textstring>Chop the flesh into 1cm dice and toss in a tablespoon of vegetable oil along with a few pinches of salt. Roast in the oven at gas mark 6 for 20-30 minutes, until lightly coloured and cooked through.  </textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>     
		<text xstart="15" ystart="700" xend="1000" yend="800" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="30" fontcolor="#000000" > 
			<textbody underlined="false" bold="false" italic="false">
				<textstring>Meanwhile, add cold water to the trimmings and bring to the boil.</textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>		
        		
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/IMG_butnut_4.png" xstart="15" ystart="200" width="700" height="466" layer="2" />	
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/IMG_butnut_5.png" xstart="725" ystart="200" width="700" height="466" layer="2" />		
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/slideBackground.png" xstart="0" ystart="0" width="1440" height="900" layer="0" />
	</slide>

	<slide id="3" duration="30" lastSlide="false">
		<text xstart="10" ystart="10" xend="1000" yend="300" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="40" fontcolor="#000000" > 
			<textbody underlined="false" bold="true" italic="false">
        		<textstring>Step Three</textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>
		<text xstart="15" ystart="100" xend="750" yend="400" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="30" fontcolor="#000000" >
			<textbody >
        		<textstring>Simmer for 15-20 minutes then strain into another pan. This creates a lightly flavoured squash stock. </textstring>
      			</textbody>
        </text>
        <text xstart="700" ystart="550" xend="1300" yend="400" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="30" fontcolor="#000000" >
			<textbody >
        		<textstring>Wash and dry the seeds, and lightly toast in a dry pan. </textstring>
      			</textbody>
        </text>
        
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/IMG_butnut_6.png" xstart="700" ystart="70" width="650" height="433" layer="3" />
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/IMG_butnut_7.png" xstart="15" ystart="360" width="650" height="433" layer="3" />
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/slideBackground.png" xstart="0" ystart="0" width="1440" height="900" layer="0" />
					
	</slide>

	<slide id="4" duration="30" lastSlide="false">
		<text xstart="10" ystart="10" xend="1000" yend="300" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="40" fontcolor="#000000" > 
			<textbody underlined="false" bold="true" italic="false">
        		<textstring>Step Four</textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>
		<text xstart="15" ystart="70" xend="1400" yend="200" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="30" fontcolor="#000000" orientation="0"> 
			<textbody underlined="false" bold="false" italic="false">
        		<textstring>Add the roasted butternut squash to a pan, as well as enough stock to cover. Bring to the boil then blend with the butter using the best equipment available to you.</textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>  
		<text xstart="750" ystart="650" xend="1300" yend="1000" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="30" fontcolor="#000000" orientation="0"> 
			<textbody underlined="false" bold="false" italic="false">
        		<textstring>Pass through a fine sieve then check the seasoning, adding salt and pepper to taste.</textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>     		
        		
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/IMG_butnut_8.png" xstart="100" ystart="150" width="550" height="366" layer="2" />	
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/IMG_butnut_9.png" xstart="750" ystart="150" width="550" height="366" layer="2" />		
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/IMG_butnut_10.png" xstart="150" ystart="520" width="550" height="366" layer="2" />				
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/slideBackground.png" xstart="0" ystart="0" width="1440" height="900" layer="0" />
	</slide>
	
	<slide id="5" duration="30" lastSlide="false">
		<text xstart="10" ystart="10" xend="1000" yend="300" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="40" fontcolor="#000000" > 
			<textbody underlined="false" bold="true" italic="false">
        		<textstring>Step Five</textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>
		
		<text xstart="10" ystart="100" xend="1000" yend="300" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="30" fontcolor="#000000" orientation="0">
			<textbody >
        		<textstring>To serve, reheat the soup and pour into a bowl.</textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>
			
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/IMG_butnut_11.png" xstart="15" ystart="150" width="700" height="466" layer="2" />	
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/IMG_butnut_12.png" xstart="725" ystart="250" width="700" height="466" layer="2" />		
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/slideBackground.png" xstart="0" ystart="0" width="1440" height="900" layer="0" />
	</slide>

	<slide id="6" duration="30" lastSlide="true">
		<text xstart="10" ystart="10" xend="1000" yend="300" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="40" fontcolor="#000000" > 
			<textbody underlined="false" bold="true" italic="false">
        		<textstring>Eat.</textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>
		<text xstart="350" ystart="750" xend="1000" yend="300" font="Helvetica Neue Thin" fontsize="30" fontcolor="#000000" orientation="0">
			<textbody >
        		<textstring>Top with a teaspoon of the toasted seeds.</textstring>
      			</textbody>
		</text>
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/IMG_butnut_13.png" xstart="250" ystart="100" width="900" height="600" layer="7" />			
		<image urlname="Butternut Squash Soup/slideBackground.png" xstart="0" ystart="0" width="1440" height="900" layer="0" />
	</slide>

</slideshow>